{"tid":866883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個你曾經最窮時刻","createTime":"2018-10-18T08:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T08:49:16.000Z","uid":71915,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8d1476b42269aa307b272e389727fcc98ca46f","tid":866883,"uid":71915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"試過成個月<br />\n<br />\n日日都係食生命面包搽榛子醬做lunch/dinner<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSkip早餐<br />\n<br />\n好彩間中有屋企飯食先無死"},{"pid":"55d51f06c647a022470307eee9c64e8501f95072","tid":866883,"uid":156986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"呢啲post精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5a84df523163287c5f0d346e744e63255de70d","tid":866883,"uid":144776,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"你仲有錢買榛子醬...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bcdb77935255c837107a387afa3e9cad51e012","tid":866883,"uid":212026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:30:33.000Z","msg":"食自己啲精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10e94bb947465112285caaf31d9b2bbc8fd51b8","tid":866883,"uid":100766,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"失業嗰時最窮<br />\n搞到要阿媽幫我俾八達通條數<br />\n又出張附屬卡俾我碌<br />\n仲語重心長咁質多張廿蚊紙摺好俾我責袋<br />\n仲有買啲玉返黎俾我戴話旺吓我<br />\n諗起自己當時真係好冇用.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過咗10年，嗰張廿蚊仲喺我銀包<br />\n多謝阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17dde184fbac4f423a44d0b268431465c89b66ea","tid":866883,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a4b62fe3aad15df974bf8c51e33cba7874b18ad","tid":866883,"uid":27596,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"手頭1蚊都冇<br />\n冇人幫<br />\n退咗張八達通買20蚊六合彩<br />\n兩支大青島  熱嘅<br />\n飲住等開六合彩<br />\n最後中咗9600<br />\n可以繼續到我嘅人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3838f654f4c9f147f1fb5d82247fe2e54147610d","tid":866883,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:44:37.000Z","msg":"最窮個陣人在日本住<br />\n戶口得唔夠15000YEN但要用成個月，<br />\n早餐唔食<br />\n中午避開D同學返屋企食麵包<br />\n夜晚自己煮<br />\n<br />\n完全無得出去玩<br />\n打工D糧又未出<br />\n諗起個陣真係陰公到想喊"},{"pid":"8329aa54b1e6a214e10b43de15166cf84061ff0b","tid":866883,"uid":71915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a5a84df523163287c5f0d346e744e63255de70d","tid":866883,"uid":144776,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"你仲有錢買榛子醬...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:47:24.000Z","msg":"白面包真係好難食...<br />\n<br />\n一罐榛子醬可以食好耐！又好食！"},{"pid":"2e5bc57772603282dd988982f843c9230b27456b","tid":866883,"uid":185686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:48:14.000Z","msg":"我成個銀包淨返10蚊<br />\n果時咁好彩啲人完左活動剩左一箱就過期既嘉頓餐包<br />\n俾我捱左一個星期"},{"pid":"96495d46341f2353c4d06cf5974fca9548f364ad","tid":866883,"uid":152147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T08:49:16.000Z","msg":"戶口98蚊 打電話叫朋友過住2蚊黎先"}]}